=============================
=  README for ex4: hangman=
=============================


==================
=  Description:  =
==================
Hangman is a game for one player that tries to guess a random word that choosen by the computer by suggesting letters in English, within a certain number of wrong guesses. The player needs to guess the word before the computer completes the hangman

======================
=  Special Comments  =
======================
If we wanted to play the game with Hebrew letters so we had to modify the function 'if_letter' with a list with Alphabetical letters and a different length. And also change the functions: 'letter_to_index' and ' index_to_letter'